summary:
Thanks to you I chose to stay
Instead of taking my life away, 
I don’t even know what to say
But I‘m thankful for you everyday....
body:
THANKS TO TAYLOR 🖤


Thanks to you I chose to stay

Instead of taking my life away,

I don’t even know what to say

But I‘m thankful for you everyday.


Thanks to you I feel amazing,

You are inspiring and generous.

I will always listen when you sing,

Because you’re always there for us,

The sound of your voice comforting

At concerts that are adventurous.


Thanks to you I decided to start

Creating my very own art,

Even though we are apart

You are forever in my heart.


My love for you is wide as the ocean,

Pictures of you above my bed.

All our moments in slow motion,

Memories of you inside my head.

You made me forget my caution

And rise up from the dead.


My love for you won’t ever end,

You taught me to uncover lies.

I‘d reply to every message send,

Cause you give me your best advice.


My love for you wasn’t a choice,

It just came to clean up the mess

Of my own head‘s terrible noise.

You came into my world and I confess

That I’m afraid of using my voice,

But thanks to you I‘m fearless.


I wish you knew

That I love you,

I say it because it’s true:

Thank you! ♥️



@taylorswift @taylornation 💋🐾

LESSON TEN: Try cooking Ina Garten’s Real Meatballs & Spaghetti

TAYLOR TAYLOR TAYLOOOOR!! We made the Ina Garten recipe you recommended! My Mom was confused when I INSISTED we only use ground beef and packaged bread crumbs but you’re right, they do taste great with those changes. The recipe also made THIRTEEN MEATBALLS, not sure if you were watching over us somehow to make that happen but it swiftly made it even more amazing! Thank you for the best Sunday night meal suggestion!!

question: I don't think I've seen this posted, but QuikClot gave a comment after Taylor's Elle Us article that name-checked it this week: “We’re grateful to Taylor Swift for shining a light upon the need for preparedness and access to bleeding control supplies. It is our hope that this leads to more awareness of this important topic, as QuikClot dressing is just one tool among many used to make our communities safer,” a rep for the company told The Blast. theblast*com/taylor-swift-quikclot-gunshot/
answer: When Taylor Swift mentions you in an article, you go and get that promo for yourself 😉 Here’s the article you mentioned…
